      ### The Fan

      Papery opponent  
      You adorn her smile as  
      She poses with a certain ease

      Swift strokes  
      Excite the air and flutter  
      Over lips of damson

      Breathing zephyr  
      Across caressed cheeks  
      Boast no more.

