      ### Giselle

      Minx; eyes bound shut  
      Hands, soft that you bring  
      Are playful with a feline elegance

      Crystalline gaze  
      Falls upon unread features  
      Silent whispers turn to brutal panting

      I am yours to keep  
      Wounded by your venom.

